      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "NUTS THEN BOLTS (7) produced an impressive win last time in quickest of the meeting when scoring by 5.5 lengths (22.63) at this track. Rates a top chance again. REBORN PASSION (8) flew the lids off the inside draw with a fast early split last time and went on to clock 22.91 when a nose winner over 400m at this track. The form from her last run stacks up well. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. SAMARA ROSE (1) took advantage of the inside draw with an all-the-way win last start (22.95) at this track in a Maiden over 400m. Won at her only start from this box. Makes plenty of appeal if runs up to latest. BUSHLAND BOY (2) cannot be overlooked following a recent top-three finish here at this distance.",
